h1. Curious about coming to the talk?

you don't need any rails or git experience, just some interest in both. You will probably get the most out of the talk if you have some web design experience, but it might also be useful for _project managers_ or _business executives_ that are interested in the topic.

h1. Instructions for viewing

to view the slide show open the file output/presentation.index.html with a web browser. 

Alert boxes are from embedded youTube videos. If its annoying, load from your localhost web server to get around the security sandbox of flash.